#originalTopic=Debate:_Public_insurance_option_in_US_health_care
US health care is fantastic, but millions can't afford it. Edward Kennedy. "Health bill would fix what's broken". Boston Globe. May 28, 2009: "We have the greatest doctors and medical innovations in the world, but more and more Americans are on the outside looking in to a world of progress and discovery that is denied to them because they cannot afford quality healthcare."
